HEADWORD: Counterclaim
<hw>Coun"ter*claim`</hw> <pr>(-kl⟦amac⟧m`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A claim made by a person as an offset to a claim
made on him.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

